Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:29.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信  愛之共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:38.46,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}擁夜入眠  殘月鳴泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.78,0:22:44.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫輪回  惑月迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:50.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}滿盈圓缺  無痕冰消
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:57.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心結  若縛君影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:03.51,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}則至神允  墜天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:07.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}深信此愛  永不相棄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:15.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}細語聲中憶往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:20.86,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛恨交結暗之樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:27.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相連
