Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:59.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}接連著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:12.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心口難開 「君莫泣」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.94,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漸次斑駁  世界之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:25.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}身在旅途　至終焉之河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:31.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}刹那之間  逢見君影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:35.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如日削月割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:47.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}故鄉迢迢  時之彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與君共往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無愛無心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:03:05.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夜之彼方  如幻蒼空
